Scarlet Heart
Episode 9

24
00:02:22,167 --> 00:02:25,633
Your Majesty, you were too worked up,

25
00:02:25,633 --> 00:02:27,633
that's why your qi couldn't flow smoothly.

26
00:02:27,633 --> 00:02:31,800
Later, I will get you some calming medicine.

27
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:34,533
After taking the medication, Your Majesty should rest well,

28
00:02:34,533 --> 00:02:36,167
then you will naturally recover from the illness.

29
00:02:36,167 --> 00:02:39,600
But extreme emotions will harm your health. Grief and anger--

30
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:41,467
Imperial Father, your son is unfilial!

31
00:02:41,467 --> 00:02:43,233
I was unable to help share the burden of your worries!

32
00:02:43,233 --> 00:02:45,267
Even when the Crown Prince did things disgraceful to the country,

33
00:02:45,267 --> 00:02:47,600
- I deserve to die!
- Fourth Prince.

34
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:49,100
I am here.

35
00:02:49,100 --> 00:02:51,400
Find someone to keep watch over the Crown Prince.

36
00:02:52,600 --> 00:02:56,400
As for the rest of the matters, do as you see fit.

37
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,600
Your son receives your orders.

38
00:03:09,567 --> 00:03:11,400
Fourth Brother,

39
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,767
regarding this matter of the Crown Prince,

40
00:03:12,767 --> 00:03:14,533
how are you planning on dealing with it?

41
00:03:15,467 --> 00:03:16,700
This isn't an easy task.

42
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:20,667
The Crown Prince, he was just asking for it.

43
00:03:20,667 --> 00:03:22,700
Are you still going to defend him?

44
00:03:23,440 --> 00:03:24,333
Thirteenth Brother.

45
00:03:24,333 --> 00:03:25,667
What I'm saying is the truth.

46
00:03:25,667 --> 00:03:27,233
The Crown Prince is arrogant and wilful.

47
00:03:27,233 --> 00:03:30,667
Even though Imperial Father and you try to help and protect him,

48
00:03:30,667 --> 00:03:32,100
even after so many lessons, he hasn't improved,

49
00:03:32,100 --> 00:03:33,800
continuing to act recklessly and brazenly.

50
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:36,733
This time, he did something that embarrasses our country and humiliated our Imperial Father.

51
00:03:36,733 --> 00:03:39,133
Even Imperial Father wants to punish him severely.

52
00:03:39,133 --> 00:03:42,133
Fourth Brother, are you still going to defend him?

53
00:03:42,133 --> 00:03:43,800
The deposing of him this time

54
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:46,100
might be the result of Imperial Father's momentary anger.

55
00:03:46,100 --> 00:03:48,400
No one can predict what changes will take place in the future.

56
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:50,067
We should just do what we're told

57
00:03:50,067 --> 00:03:52,367
and follow Imperial Father's orders.

58
00:03:52,367 --> 00:03:54,933
As for other matters, there's no need for us to meddle with them.

59
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:05,100
Just now, outside Qianqing Palace,

60
00:04:05,100 --> 00:04:07,733
I saw the ministers talking about the Crown Prince being deposed.

61
00:04:07,733 --> 00:04:10,633
Even the Internal Minister Wang who's always been calm and collected

62
00:04:10,633 --> 00:04:12,133
was busy trying to learn of the latest news.

63
00:04:12,133 --> 00:04:13,500
He didn't even watch where he was going

64
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:15,100
and bumped right into Minister Feng.

65
00:04:15,100 --> 00:04:16,967
His Minister hat almost fell off!

66
00:04:16,967 --> 00:04:18,700
It made me laugh so hard!

67
00:04:18,700 --> 00:04:19,767
Really?

68
00:04:19,767 --> 00:04:21,733
How could Minister Wang have been so lacking in decorum?

69
00:04:21,733 --> 00:04:23,867
Usually, Minister Wang's so strait-laced,

70
00:04:23,867 --> 00:04:25,133
wouldn't he have been very embarrassed?

71
00:04:25,133 --> 00:04:26,233
That is of course!

72
00:04:26,233 --> 00:04:27,767
That really is so funny!

73
00:04:27,767 --> 00:04:28,967
We might think it's funny,

74
00:04:28,967 --> 00:04:30,667
but the Ministers certainly don't think so.

75
00:04:30,667 --> 00:04:33,133
Just because of this matter of the Crown Prince's deposal?

76
00:04:34,267 --> 00:04:36,633
This matter of his deposal is no small matter!

77
00:04:36,633 --> 00:04:37,900
With the position of Crown Prince empty,

78
00:04:37,900 --> 00:04:41,333
the Ministers are all contemplating on which prince's camp they should side.

79
00:04:42,520 --> 00:04:44,000
They only have one betting chip,

80
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,640
so they mustn't put their bets on the wrong person.

81
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:47,840
Naturally, they're floundering as to what to do.

82
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:50,240
But surely we can't be without a Crown Prince?

83
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:53,560
Sister, in your opinion, which prince do you think is the most likely to become the Crown Prince?

84
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,760
Eighth Prince of course!

85
00:04:54,760 --> 00:04:56,680
When His Majesty gave him the job of supervising state affairs,

86
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:59,100
all the ministers praised him for being both capable and virtuous,

87
00:04:59,100 --> 00:05:00,560
and that he has the makings of a good Emperor.

88
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,560
I don't agree.

89
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:03,400
Fourteenth Prince is handsome and extraordinary

90
00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:04,600
and he's also good at fighting wars.

91
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:06,440
I think that Fourteenth Prince is the most likely one.

92
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:08,120
You're wrong. If we're talking about bravery,

93
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:10,120
Thirteenth Prince is just as brave as Fourteenth Prince.

94
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:11,160
Actually,

95
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:13,320
the First Prince is still the First Prince.

96
00:05:13,320 --> 00:05:15,560
If we go according to seniority, it might be First Prince.

97
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:18,000
In your opinion,

98
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,920
which prince do you think is the most suitable.

99
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:21,180
As to who will be Crown Prince,

100
00:05:21,180 --> 00:05:22,720
within His Majesty's heart, he definitely has ideas of who to appoint.

101
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:24,920
It's not something for us servants to discuss.

102
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:27,080
We need to only know our place

103
00:05:27,080 --> 00:05:28,380
and make sure our work is properly done.

104
00:05:28,380 --> 00:05:29,800
No matter who becomes the master,

105
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:31,200
we should do our best to take care of him.

106
00:05:31,200 --> 00:05:33,000
Talk less and do more work.

107
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,320
Don't be a busybody.

108
00:05:34,320 --> 00:05:37,240
What an apt saying. "Don't be a busybody".

109
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:40,360
- Eunuch Li.
- Teacher.

110
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:43,720
All of you should learn from Rouxi.

111
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:45,680
Thanks for your praise, Eunuch Li.

112
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:47,840
I just want to live peacefully.

113
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:48,760
There are still many matters

114
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:50,360
in which I will need Eunuch Li to teach me.

115
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:52,680
You already know to act discreetly so as to keep yourself safe,

116
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:54,620
what else do you need me to teach you?

117
00:05:54,620 --> 00:05:57,160
In the palace, it's hard to predict one's future,

118
00:05:57,160 --> 00:06:00,000
I'll still need Eunuch Li to take good care of me in many matters.

119
00:06:01,320 --> 00:06:03,620
All right. All of you get on with your work.

120
00:06:03,620 --> 00:06:05,360
Yes.

121
00:06:10,420 --> 00:06:12,200
Ruoxi!

122
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:21,600
- Greetings to Fourteenth Prince.
- Excused.

123
00:06:29,340 --> 00:06:31,660
Although Eighth Brother has many matters that are keeping him busy,

124
00:06:31,660 --> 00:06:32,840
he insistently reminded me

125
00:06:32,840 --> 00:06:34,520
to pass this letter to you.

126
00:06:34,520 --> 00:06:36,140
He even insisted that I hand it to you personally,

127
00:06:36,140 --> 00:06:37,320
and ensure that you receive it in good condition.

128
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:43,960
In my opinion, to Eighth Brother,

129
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:46,400
you are just as important as state affairs.

